  m_text: "\tMy name is Ibrahim Emre Bas. On this site, I'll be sharing the games
    and projects I've been working on, as well as posting news and updates. You can
    see my other accounts and links down below.\n\n\n\n\n\nSome websites you see
    here\u2026 don't exist yet!! It's year 2000, remember? You might ask yourself:
    \"What the hell are these links??\" Well\u2026 just wait 10\u201320 years. Then
    you'll get it!"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a026544f366ba7e4d87cdea1457d5ee9, type: 2}
