      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Hello visitor. Welcome to my website!\n\n\tMy name is Ibrahim Emre Bas
    (Synthesizer) and I just graduated as a computer engineer (yeah, finally!). I'm
    super into game development \u2013 it's what I do, what I breathe, and what I
    stay up until 3 AM for xD\r\n\r\n\tOn this site, I'll be sharing the games and
    small projects I've been working on. You'll also find news, updates, and random
    stuff I'm messing around with. Some of my projects are down below \u2013 check
    'em out!\r\n\r\nThanks for stopping by. It really means a lot.\r\nAnd hey\u2026
    don't forget to sign my Guestbook! "
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a026544f366ba7e4d87cdea1457d5ee9, type: 2}
